name: UMovieSceneSequence
doc: Abstract base class for movie scene animations (C++ version).

methods.name: FindBindingByTag
methods.doc: Find the first object binding ID associated with the specified tag name (set up through RMB->Expose on Object bindings from within sequencer)

methods.name: FindBindingsByTag
methods.doc: Find all object binding IDs associated with the specified tag name (set up through RMB->Expose on Object bindings from within sequencer)

methods.name: GetEarliestTimecodeSource
methods.doc: Get the earliest timecode source out of all of the movie scene sections contained within this sequence's movie scene.
